name: Stunning Castle Converted Monastery
description: A medieval luxury restored monastery placed in the middle of a forest, on a quiet hill of the Umbrian countryside hosts a 3-storey property with a shared seasonal (May-October) swimming pool. Perfect for a night of rest before continuing on the walking trail...or for a full holiday of peace, relaxation and enjoyment.
